Dialogue: 0,1:37:05.81,1:37:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,X-Rays down.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.86,1:37:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}ROSS{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b} What about Echo?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.53,1:37:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She's alive, under control.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.53,1:37:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Who planned this?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:13.32,1:37:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Go fuck yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.49,1:37:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}SCREAMING{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.25,1:37:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this, eh? Your next bomb?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.04,1:37:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go fuck yourself.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.58,1:37:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}SCREAMING{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.21,1:37:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk, you rotten slag!
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.88,1:37:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}SCREAMING{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.30,1:37:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}SOBBING{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.31,1:37:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:42.43,1:37:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine minutes it blows. No time to land.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.06,1:37:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,- What's that? A plane? Which plane?\N- {\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}SPITS{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.36,1:37:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Which plane?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:51.19,1:37:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}RICE{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b} Open her shirt.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:59.12,1:38:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}ELECTRICITY CRACKLES{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:00.37,1:38:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This is how it works.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.95,1:38:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask questions. You answer.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.92,1:38:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Flight 136 to Rome.\NPassenger name Ian Wood.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:12.01,1:38:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Bomb's in his laptop.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.30,1:38:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Set to go off at 3:00 p.m. exactly.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.51,1:38:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}ANNOUNCER{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b} Ladies and gentlemen,\Nplease be advised.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:18.22,1:38:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Flight 136 to Rome\Nhas been further delayed.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.72,1:38:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We apologize for the inconvenience.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.85,1:38:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Again, Flight 136 to Rome...
Dialogue: 0,1:38:26.27,1:38:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}OFFICER{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b} Ian Wood!\NIs there an Ian Wood here?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.27,1:38:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian Wood! Ian Wood?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:31.65,1:38:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there an Ian Wood here? Ian Wood?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.11,1:38:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ian Wood? Ian Wood? Ian Wood?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:40.70,1:38:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:42.70,1:38:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They're looking for someone\Nnamed Ian Wood.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:45.04,1:38:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me. I'm Ian Wood.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:47.25,1:38:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}OFFICER{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b} Ian Wood!
Dialogue: 0,1:38:49.13,1:38:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ian Wood.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:51.59,1:38:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}PANTING{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b} Is that your laptop?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:55.17,1:38:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,- Move! Move! Move!\N- {\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}PEOPLE SCREAMING{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:38:57.22,1:39:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down! Get down! Get down! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.47,1:39:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:02.85,1:39:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down! Get down!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:04.64,1:39:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Move! Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.27,1:39:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down! Get down! Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:07.89,1:39:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outta the way! Get out!\NMove here! Get out! {\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}GROANS{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.94,1:39:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.53,1:39:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}GRUNTS{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:39:35.84,1:39:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}JOKER{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b} She said a gas man turned up\Nwith an assault gun, a Chinaman.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:39.68,1:39:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Started shooting, killed everyone but her,\Nand then walked out the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:43.05,1:39:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She said he was a Chinaman?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.60,1:39:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Affirmative. About 60 years old.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.64,1:39:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}ROSS{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b} Just got word\Nthe device is neutralized.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.48,1:39:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work. Fox Hunt is now terminated.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:51.86,1:39:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No loose ends.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:53.52,1:39:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:03.12,1:40:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}DOG BARKS{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:05.74,1:40:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}BROMLEY{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b} It's Bromley. I need an AP\Nout to all city-district units
Dialogue: 0,1:40:09.25,1:40:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,from Wapping High Street to the A1203.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.92,1:40:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Suspect's an Asian male, 61 years of age,\Nfive feet, eight inches, 11 stone.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.55,1:40:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,His name's Ngoc Minh Quan.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.55,1:40:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He's armed\Nand has U.S. Special Forces training.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.72,1:40:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Use extreme caution.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.24,1:40:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}SIGHS{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.41,1:40:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}CELL PHONE VIBRATING{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.38,1:40:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:55.46,1:40:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on the flight\Nthey targeted to blow up.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:58.42,1:41:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of your timely information,\Nwe stopped it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:00.30,1:41:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to thank you personally.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.55,1:41:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God you're OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.60,1:41:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}DAVIES{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b} The bombers were neutralized,\Neven Sara McKay,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.10,1:41:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,whom you called "Maggie."
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.65,1:41:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She gave a reporter the bomb\Nthat was to have been put on my flight.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.65,1:41:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She also carried out the bus carnage,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.94,1:41:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and is directly connected to you,\Nand McGrath.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:25.12,1:41:27.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have call-pens going\Nto and from her off the cell tower
Dialogue: 0,1:41:27.95,1:41:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,by your farm and town homes.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.62,1:41:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 250 precision locations\Nand activations
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.25,1:41:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,- consistent with your mutual activities.\N- Katherine...
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.92,1:41:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I've spoken to the PM.\NHe's agreed to keep you in office for now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:38.21,1:41:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm issuing pardons\Nfor five On-the-Runs, one is your cousin.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.13,1:41:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But, make no mistake,\NDeputy First Minister, you are ours now.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.05,1:41:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I say jump, you say where.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:48.68,1:41:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're on the next flight back to London.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:50.52,1:41:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow you'll brief\NSO15 and myself on everything you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:54.77,1:41:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.56,1:41:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}LINE DISCONNECTS{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.59,1:42:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}DOORBELL RINGING{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.20,1:42:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, sir.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:30.16,1:43:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you find me?
Dialogue: 0,1:43:32.95,1:43:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I gave you the names, like I said.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.83,1:43:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This woman, she's a bomber.\NYou lie. You plan everything.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.84,1:43:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,For whatever it's worth...
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.88,1:43:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I never intended to hurt your daughter
Dialogue: 0,1:43:51.34,1:43:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,or any of those people.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:55.93,1:43:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Send.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.31,1:44:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,1:44:12.16,1:44:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\b1\c&HFF759B&}({\c} {\fnMistral\c&H00FF80&}CHIMES{\fn\c} {\c&HFF759B&}){\c\b}
Dialogue: 0,1:44:16.29,1:44:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's now on the Internet,\Nyou and your mistress.
